title: 253: Mobility, Anxiety & Depression, Organ Donation & MORE
description: It's Q&A time once again! Sal, Adam & Justin answer Pump Head questions about integrating mobility into a workout, the goal of doing a physique/bodybuilding type show just once for the experience, dealing with a client's or their own anxiety and depression, what made them outstanding trainers & becoming a living organ donor. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpmedia.com
